
## build from docker
```bash
docker build ./ -t aceso
docker run -it -d --name=aceso-ae --net=host --ipc=host --gpus=all -v ./:/workspace/aceso aceso bash
docker exec -it aceso-ae bash
```

#### issue
```bash
pip3 install -v --disable-pip-version-check --no-cache-dir --global-option="--cpp_ext" --global-option="--cuda_ext"  ./

error
```
run

```bash
pip3 install packaging>=22.0 # refer to https://github.com/pypa/setuptools/issues/4483
```


